  "title": "I could not find what I was looking for",
  "body": "I am trying to utilize instantsearch.js for something that doesn't appear to be very clear in the documentation or possible.\r\n\r\nMy use case is that I have a product catalog and using the connectors, I have refiners and a search box to get the correct results. However, what I need to do is add another filter to my query saying 'give me all the products that are missing the attribute 'device'.\r\n\r\nIs it possible (using instantsearch.js preferably) to search my algolia indice for records that are missing an attribute?",
